\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Could you tell me your full name please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 My full name before I married was Katherine Margaret Hengus, now it's Katherine Margaret Bairnson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 And your present address?
