\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 That's all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Yes, yes, that and Shetland, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Did you say the year of your birth was 1903?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Yes.
