\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 The non-crofters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Yes, yes, we were cotters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Did }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1513370\charrsid9600179 crofters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 
 sometimes stay on the croft land and build their house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Well o
ur house was built on my grandfather's croft. In fact, the time that it was built there was the three crofts together but they just - you know, they'd be small narrow strips, narrow strips, one had this narrow strip and the next one had this narrow strip 
and another one had this narrow strip so that our house really came to be, I think, on all three of the neighbours but - it was really three brothers, my grandfather and two of his brothers. Who had the crofts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 When a man was a cotter did he get anything from the land?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Oh no. He'd no right to anything, no, no, he'd no right to anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Was he never able to keep a cow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13267250 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Just a house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2850780 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2909418\charrsid9600179 Just a house, yes, just a house.
